1. Develop and deliver medicines that can cure or prevent all diseases;
2. Promote, fund and protect research across all academic fields, and teach children to be lifelong learners;
3. Encourage investment in technologies that enable the Earth to feed and provide clean water and energy to a growing global population;
4. Encourage a scalable plant-based food system;
5. Invest in clean water systems and energy solutions that are robust, accessible, and aren't just for the wealthy;
6. Promote the preservation of environments, habitats, and biodiversity;
